{"TopicId":153453,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Loss of FPS when KSP is unfocussed","CreatedByName":"endernite54","CreatedById":171902,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-13T11:27:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"endernite54","CreatedById":171902,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-13T11:27:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello ! A strange problem appeared two weeks ago, no significant change to the game were made and reinstalling it didn\u0027t fix the issue !\u003Cbr\u003E\nI play KSP in full screen mode, and when I unfocus KSP (opening my browser, alt-tabbing etc..) the game starts to lag tremendously, I get like 3 FPS... Which is really inconvenient as you may imagine !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have Kerbal Engineer, SSTU, persistent rotation, probes plus, decals, Direct launch vehicles and Space shuttle payloads.. Running ksp in vanilla doesn\u0027t fix the problem, I\u0027ve checked the logs, no errors when the lag occurs...\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood day,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Luca\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-12-13T11:27:26Z\u0022 title=\u002212/13/2016 11:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 13, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by endernite54\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-14T15:41:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/171902-endernite54/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022171902\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/171902-endernite54/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@endernite54\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know there used to be, and there might still be a setting\u00A0for KSP running in the background. Turning that off might help if you don\u0027t\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eneed\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0the game running while you\u0027re multitasking.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. That setting might only be referring to when you \u0022pause\u0022 the game. I can\u0027t remember.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-12-14T16:39:49Z\u0022 title=\u002212/14/2016 04:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Gianni1122\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"How to: KSP","CreatedById":163894,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-14T15:45:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222887476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153453\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481730073\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022170752\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gianni1122\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Gianni1122 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know there used to be, and there might still be a setting\u00A0for KSP running in the background. Turning that off might help if you don\u0027t\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eneed\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0the game running while you\u0027re multitasking.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. That setting might only be referring to when you \u0022pause\u0022 the game. I can\u0027t remember.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe setting is called \u0022Simulate in Background\u0022 I believe; it is in the graphics section\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-14T16:16:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/163894-how-to-ksp/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022163894\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/163894-how-to-ksp/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@How to: KSP\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"endernite54","CreatedById":171902,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-20T12:26:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222887481\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153453\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481730305\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163894\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022How to: KSP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 14/12/2016 at 4:45 PM, How to: KSP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe setting is called \u0022Simulate in Background\u0022 I believe; it is in the graphics section\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOHH... Thank you ! That really was an issue, thanks a lot \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSant\u00E9 !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"How to: KSP","CreatedById":163894,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-20T17:56:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222894274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153453\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221482236770\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022endernite54\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, endernite54 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOHH... Thank you ! That really was an issue, thanks a lot \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSant\u00E9 !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour welcome, m8 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}